{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":496,"text":"As you might imagine, I'm absolutely passionate"},{"time":1989,"text":"about dance. I'm passionate about making it,"},{"time":4194,"text":"about watching it, about encouraging others"},{"time":6798,"text":"to participate in it,"},{"time":8667,"text":"and I'm also really passionate about creativity."},{"time":11290,"text":"Creativity for me is something that's absolutely critical,"},{"time":15407,"text":"and I think it's something that you can teach."},{"time":17792,"text":"I think the technicities of creativity can be taught"},{"time":20053,"text":"and shared, and I think you can find out things"},{"time":22219,"text":"about your own personal physical signature,"},{"time":24488,"text":"your own cognitive habits, and use that as"},{"time":26400,"text":"a point of departure to misbehave beautifully."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29852,"text":"I was born in the 1970s, and John Travolta was big"},{"time":34255,"text":"in those days: \"Grease,\" \"Saturday Night Fever,\""},{"time":36726,"text":"and he provided a fantastic kind of male role model for me"},{"time":39403,"text":"to start dancing. My parents were very up for me going."},{"time":42183,"text":"They absolutely encouraged me to take risks, to go,"},{"time":45045,"text":"to try, to try. I had an opportunity, an access"},{"time":49270,"text":"to a local dance studio, and I had an enlightened teacher"},{"time":52861,"text":"who allowed me to make up my own and invent"},{"time":55966,"text":"my own dances, so what she did was let me make up"},{"time":58960,"text":"my own ballroom and Latin American dances to teach"},{"time":61909,"text":"to my peers."},{"time":63281,"text":"And that was the very first time that I found an opportunity"},{"time":66050,"text":"to feel that I was able to express my own voice,"},{"time":68935,"text":"and that's what's fueled me, then, to become a choreographer."},{"time":71753,"text":"I feel like I've got something to say and something to share."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74769,"text":"And I guess what's interesting is, is that I am now obsessed"},{"time":78346,"text":"with the technology of the body."},{"time":79933,"text":"I think it's the most technologically literate thing that we have,"},{"time":83229,"text":"and I'm absolutely obsessed with finding a way"},{"time":86328,"text":"of communicating ideas through the body to audiences"},{"time":89626,"text":"that might move them, touch them,"},{"time":91779,"text":"help them think differently about things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94881,"text":"So for me, choreography is very much a process"},{"time":97483,"text":"of physical thinking. It's very much in mind,"},{"time":100892,"text":"as well as in body, and it's a collaborative process."},{"time":104155,"text":"It's something that I have to do with other people."},{"time":105981,"text":"You know, it's a distributed cognitive process in a way."},{"time":108735,"text":"I work often with designers and visual artists,"},{"time":111333,"text":"obviously dancers and other choreographers,"},{"time":113941,"text":"but also, more and more, with economists,"},{"time":118312,"text":"anthropologists, neuroscientists, cognitive scientists,"},{"time":122618,"text":"people really who come from very different domains of"},{"time":125385,"text":"expertise, where they bring their intelligence to bear"},{"time":128378,"text":"on a different kind of creative process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130766,"text":"What I thought we would do today a little bit is"},{"time":133969,"text":"explore this idea of physical thinking,"},{"time":136230,"text":"and we're all experts in physical thinking."},{"time":138031,"text":"Yeah, you all have a body, right?"},{"time":139409,"text":"And we all know what that body is like in the real world,"},{"time":141600,"text":"so one of the aspects of physical thinking"},{"time":143294,"text":"that we think about a lot is this notion of proprioception,"},{"time":146208,"text":"the sense of my own body in the space in the real world."},{"time":149273,"text":"So, we all understand what it feels like to know"},{"time":152659,"text":"where the ends of your fingers are"},{"time":154012,"text":"when you hold out your arms, yeah?"},{"time":156009,"text":"You absolutely know that when you're going to grab a cup,"},{"time":158824,"text":"or that cup moves and you have to renavigate it."},{"time":160734,"text":"So we're experts in physical thinking already."},{"time":162692,"text":"We just don't think about our bodies very much."},{"time":164728,"text":"We only think about them when they go wrong, so, when"},{"time":167833,"text":"there's a broken arm, or when you have a heart attack,"},{"time":170071,"text":"then you become really very aware of your bodies."},{"time":172536,"text":"But how is it that we can start to think about using"},{"time":174823,"text":"choreographic thinking, kinesthetic intelligence, to arm"},{"time":178231,"text":"the ways in which we think about things more generally?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180589,"text":"What I thought I'd do is, I'd make a TED premiere."},{"time":183545,"text":"I'm not sure if this is going to be good or not."},{"time":185848,"text":"I'll just be doing it."},{"time":187823,"text":"I thought what I'd do is, I'd use three versions"},{"time":189910,"text":"of physical thinking to make something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191554,"text":"I want to introduce you. This is Paolo. This is Catarina."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194670,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":197518,"text":"They have no idea what we're going to do."},{"time":200122,"text":"So this is not the type of choreography where"},{"time":202466,"text":"I already have in mind what I'm going to make,"},{"time":204810,"text":"where I've fixed the routine in my head"},{"time":207351,"text":"and I'm just going to teach it to them,"},{"time":208941,"text":"and these so-called empty vessels are just going to learn it."},{"time":211250,"text":"That's not the methodology at all that we work with."},{"time":214184,"text":"But what's important about it is how it is that they're"},{"time":218517,"text":"grasping information, how they're taking information,"},{"time":220564,"text":"how they're using it, and how they're thinking with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222695,"text":"I'm going to start really, really simply."},{"time":224143,"text":"Usually, dance has a stimulus or stimuli, and I thought"},{"time":227120,"text":"I'd take something simple, TED logo, we can all see it,"},{"time":230224,"text":"it's quite easy to work with, and I'm going to do something"},{"time":232573,"text":"very simply, where you take one idea from a body,"},{"time":235362,"text":"and it happens to be my body, and translate that"},{"time":237366,"text":"into somebody else's body,"},{"time":239558,"text":"so it's a direct transfer, transformation of energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242912,"text":"And I'm going to imagine this, you can do this too if you like,"},{"time":245692,"text":"that I'm going to just take the letter \"T\" and I'm going"},{"time":247930,"text":"to imagine it in mind, and I'm going to place that outside in"},{"time":250805,"text":"the real world. So I absolutely see a letter \"T\" in front of me."},{"time":254709,"text":"Yeah? It's absolutely there."},{"time":256114,"text":"I can absolutely walk around it when I see it, yeah?"},{"time":259094,"text":"It has a kind of a grammar. I know what I'm going to do"},{"time":261019,"text":"with it, and I can start to describe it, so I can describe it"},{"time":263954,"text":"very simply. I can describe it in my arms, right?"},{"time":266925,"text":"So all I did was take my hand and then I move my hand."},{"time":269603,"text":"I can describe it, whoa, in my head, you know? Whoa."},{"time":271790,"text":"Okay. I can do also my shoulder. Yeah?"},{"time":274098,"text":"It gives me something to do, something to work towards."},{"time":277106,"text":"If I were to take that letter \"T\" and flatten it down"},{"time":279224,"text":"on the floor, here, maybe just off the floor,"},{"time":282160,"text":"all of a sudden I could do maybe something with my knee,"},{"time":283633,"text":"yeah? Whoa. So If I put the knee and the arms together,"},{"time":286184,"text":"I've got something physical, yeah? And I can start to build something."},{"time":289744,"text":"So what I'm going to do just for one and a half minutes or so"},{"time":292205,"text":"is I'm going to take that concept, I'm going to make something,"},{"time":294805,"text":"and the dancers behind me are going to interpret it,"},{"time":297683,"text":"they're going to snapshot it, they're going to take"},{"time":299327,"text":"aspects of it, and it's almost like I'm offloading memory"},{"time":302306,"text":"and they're holding onto memory? Yeah?"},{"time":304422,"text":"And we'll see what we come up with."},{"time":305826,"text":"So just have a little watch about how they're, how they're"},{"time":307981,"text":"accessing this and what they're doing,"},{"time":309289,"text":"and I'm just going to take this letter \"T,\" the letter \"E,\""},{"time":311250,"text":"and the letter \"D,\" to make something. Okay. Here goes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314281,"text":"So I have to get myself in the zone. Right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331877,"text":"It's a bit of a cross of my arm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340438,"text":"So all I'm doing is exploring this space of \"T\""},{"time":345089,"text":"and flashing through it with some action."},{"time":350404,"text":"I'm not remembering what I'm doing."},{"time":352807,"text":"I'm just working on my task. My task is this \"T.\""},{"time":355570,"text":"Going to watch it from the side, whoa."},{"time":360947,"text":"Strike moment."},{"time":362817,"text":"That's it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367789,"text":"So we're starting to build a phrase."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372131,"text":"So what they're doing, let's see, something like that,"},{"time":374084,"text":"so what they're doing is grasping aspects of that movement"},{"time":377231,"text":"and they're generating it into a phrase."},{"time":379136,"text":"You can see the speed is extremely quick, yeah?"},{"time":381394,"text":"I'm not asking them to copy exactly."},{"time":383684,"text":"They're using the information that they receive"},{"time":386041,"text":"to generate the beginnings of a phrase."},{"time":389357,"text":"I can watch that and that can tell me something"},{"time":391278,"text":"about how it is that they're moving."},{"time":394031,"text":"Yeah, they're super quick, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397111,"text":"So I've taken this aspect of TED and translated it"},{"time":400895,"text":"into something that's physical."},{"time":405616,"text":"Some dancers, when they're watching action,"},{"time":408200,"text":"take the overall shape, the arc of the movement,"},{"time":410675,"text":"the kinetic sense of the movement,"},{"time":412780,"text":"and use that for memory."},{"time":414375,"text":"Some work very much in specific detail."},{"time":416658,"text":"They start with small little units and build it up."},{"time":420476,"text":"Okay, you've got something? One more thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438012,"text":"So they're solving this problem for me,"},{"time":441160,"text":"having a little --"},{"time":444993,"text":"They're constructing that phrase."},{"time":446854,"text":"They have something and they're going to hold on to it,"},{"time":448330,"text":"yeah? One way of making."},{"time":450353,"text":"That's going to be my beginning in this world premiere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452709,"text":"Okay. From there I'm going to do a very different thing."},{"time":454683,"text":"So basically I'm going to make a duet."},{"time":457399,"text":"I want you to think about them as architectural objects,"},{"time":460894,"text":"so what they are, are just pure lines."},{"time":463190,"text":"They're no longer people, just pure lines, and I'm going"},{"time":465746,"text":"to work with them almost as objects to think with, yeah?"},{"time":469971,"text":"So what I'm thinking about is taking"},{"time":472448,"text":"a few physical extensions from the body as I move, and"},{"time":476373,"text":"I move them, and I do that by suggesting things to them:"},{"time":478671,"text":"If, then; if, then. Okay, so here we go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":481848,"text":"Just grab this arm."},{"time":483024,"text":"Can you place that down into the floor?"},{"time":486049,"text":"Yeah, down to the floor. Can you go underneath?"},{"time":488255,"text":"Yeah. Cat, can you put leg over that side? Yeah."},{"time":492072,"text":"Can you rotate?"},{"time":493521,"text":"Whoom, just go back to the beginning."},{"time":494637,"text":"Here we go, ready? And ... bam, bake ... (clicks metronome)"},{"time":500985,"text":"Great. Okay, from there, you're both getting up."},{"time":502909,"text":"You're both getting up. Here we go. Good, now? Them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506449,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":508018,"text":"So from there, from there, we're both getting up,"},{"time":510719,"text":"we're both getting up, going in this direction,"},{"time":511962,"text":"going underneath. Whoa, whoa, underneath."},{"time":514300,"text":"Whoa, underneath, whoo-um. Yeah? Underneath. Jump."},{"time":518264,"text":"Underneath. Jump. Paolo, kick. Don't care where. Kick."},{"time":522446,"text":"Kick, replace, change a leg. Kick, replace, change the leg."},{"time":525865,"text":"Yeah? Okay? Cat, almost get his head. Almost get his head."},{"time":529574,"text":"Whoaa. Just after it, maybe. Whoaa, whaaay, ooh."},{"time":534439,"text":"Grab her waist, come up back into her first, whoom, spin,"},{"time":538757,"text":"turn her, whoo-aa. (Snaps) Great."},{"time":540363,"text":"Okay, let's have a little go from the beginning of that."},{"time":542722,"text":"Just, let me slow down here. Fancy having eight -- (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548231,"text":"Fancy having eight hours with me in a day."},{"time":551033,"text":"So, maybe too much. So, here we go, ready, and -- (Clicks metronome)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":555539,"text":"(Clicks metronome)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":563122,"text":"Nice, good job. Yeah? Okay. (Applause)"},{"time":566263,"text":"Okay, not bad. (Applause) A little bit more?"},{"time":569261,"text":"Yeah. Just a little bit more, here we go, from that place."},{"time":572053,"text":"Separate. Face the front. Separate. Face the front."},{"time":574526,"text":"Imagine that there's a circle in front of you, yeah?"},{"time":576751,"text":"Avoid it. Avoid it. Whoom. Kick it out of the way."},{"time":581646,"text":"Kick it out of the way. Throw it into the audience. Whoom."},{"time":585735,"text":"Throw it into the audience again."},{"time":586778,"text":"We've got mental architecture, we're sharing it,"},{"time":588660,"text":"therefore solving a problem. They're enacting it."},{"time":590552,"text":"Let me just see that a little bit. Ready, and go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592735,"text":"(Clicks metronome)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":597238,"text":"Okay, brilliant. Okay, here we go. From the beginning,"},{"time":598903,"text":"can we do our phrases first? And then that."},{"time":601841,"text":"And we're going to build something now, organize it,"},{"time":603530,"text":"the phrases. Here we go. Nice and slow?"},{"time":605179,"text":"Ready and go ... um. (Clicks metronome)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":608581,"text":"(Clicks metronome)"},{"time":612977,"text":"The duet starts. (Clicks metronome)"},{"time":616661,"text":"(Clicks metronome)"},{"time":629987,"text":"So yeah, okay, good. Okay, nice, very nice. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":633424,"text":"So good. So -- (Applause)"},{"time":635134,"text":"Okay. So that was -- (Applause)"},{"time":638381,"text":"Well done. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":640275,"text":"That was the second way of working."},{"time":641834,"text":"The first one, body-to-body transfer, yeah,"},{"time":644206,"text":"with an outside mental architecture that I work with"},{"time":646954,"text":"that they hold memory with for me."},{"time":649026,"text":"The second one, which is using them as objects to think"},{"time":651264,"text":"with their architectural objects, I do a series of"},{"time":653032,"text":"provocations, I say, \"If this happens, then that."},{"time":655505,"text":"If this, if that happens -- \" I've got lots of methods like that,"},{"time":657860,"text":"but it's very, very quick, and this is a third method."},{"time":660491,"text":"They're starting it already, and this is a task-based method,"},{"time":663245,"text":"where they have the autonomy to make"},{"time":664926,"text":"all of the decisions for themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":666732,"text":"So I'd like us just to do, we're going to do a little"},{"time":667991,"text":"mental dance, a little, in this little one minute,"},{"time":671413,"text":"so what I'd love you to do is imagine,"},{"time":673312,"text":"you can do this with your eyes closed, or open, and if you"},{"time":675413,"text":"don't want to do it you can watch them, it's up to you."},{"time":677891,"text":"Just for a second, think about that word \"TED\" in front of"},{"time":681631,"text":"you, so it's in mind, and it's there right in front of your mind."},{"time":684932,"text":"What I'd like you to do is transplant that outside"},{"time":687169,"text":"into the real world, so just imagine that word \"TED\""},{"time":690712,"text":"in the real world."},{"time":693045,"text":"What I'd like you to do what that is take an aspect of it."},{"time":695985,"text":"I'm going to zone in on the \"E,\" and I'm going to"},{"time":699125,"text":"scale that \"E\" so it's absolutely massive,"},{"time":701772,"text":"so I'm scaling that \"E\" so it's absolutely massive,"},{"time":704484,"text":"and then I'm going to give it dimensionality."},{"time":705655,"text":"I'm going to think about it in 3D space. So now,"},{"time":707907,"text":"instead of it just being a letter that's in front of me,"},{"time":710380,"text":"it's a space that my body can go inside of."},{"time":713261,"text":"I now decide where I'm going to be in that space,"},{"time":715978,"text":"so I'm down on this small part of the bottom rib"},{"time":720449,"text":"of the letter \"E,\" and I'm thinking about it, and I'm imagining"},{"time":723317,"text":"this space that's really high and above. If I asked you to"},{"time":726771,"text":"reach out — you don't have to literally do it, but in mind —"},{"time":729528,"text":"reach out to the top of the \"E,\" where would you reach?"},{"time":732578,"text":"If you reach with your finger, where would it be?"},{"time":734556,"text":"If you reach with your elbow, where would it be?"},{"time":737448,"text":"If I already then said about that space that you're in,"},{"time":741345,"text":"let's infuse it with the color red, what does that do"},{"time":743704,"text":"to the body? If I then said to you, what happens if"},{"time":746430,"text":"that whole wall on the side of \"E\" collapses and you have to"},{"time":749704,"text":"use your weight to put it back up,"},{"time":751550,"text":"what would you be able to do with it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":753974,"text":"So this is a mental picture, I'm describing a mental,"},{"time":755871,"text":"vivid picture that enables dancers to make choices"},{"time":759876,"text":"for themselves about what to make."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762257,"text":"Okay, you can open your eyes if you had them closed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763692,"text":"So the dancers have been working on them."},{"time":765066,"text":"So just keep working on them for a little second."},{"time":766922,"text":"So they've been working on those mental architectures in the here."},{"time":769938,"text":"I know, I think we should keep them as a surprise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":772440,"text":"So here goes, world premiere dance. Yeah? Here we go."},{"time":775020,"text":"TED dance. Okay. Here it comes. I'm going to organize it quickly."},{"time":778541,"text":"So, you're going to do the first solo that we made,"},{"time":781825,"text":"yeah blah blah blah blah, we go into the duet, yeah,"},{"time":784624,"text":"blah blah blah blah. The next solo, blah blah blah blah,"},{"time":788374,"text":"yeah, and both at the same time, you do the last solutions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":792098,"text":"Okay? Okay. Ladies and gentlemen, world premiere,"},{"time":794640,"text":"TED dance, three versions of physical thinking. (Applause)"},{"time":797408,"text":"Well, clap afterwards, let's see if it's any good, yeah? (Laughter)"},{"time":800104,"text":"So yeah, let's clap -- yeah, let's clap afterwards."},{"time":802603,"text":"Here we go. Catarina, big moment, here we go, one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804765,"text":"(Clicks metronome)"},{"time":830146,"text":"Here it comes, Cat. (Clicks metronome)"},{"time":835357,"text":"Paolo, go. (Clicks metronome) Last you solo."},{"time":839793,"text":"The one you made. (Clicks metronome)"},{"time":843202,"text":"(Clicks metronome)"},{"time":855004,"text":"Well done. Okay, good. Super. So --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":856963,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":858844,"text":"So -- (Applause)"},{"time":861135,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":862926,"text":"So -- three versions. (Applause) Oh. (Laughs)"},{"time":871911,"text":"(Applause) Three versions of physical thinking, yeah?"},{"time":874892,"text":"Three versions of physical thinking. I'm hoping that today,"},{"time":877851,"text":"what you're going to do is go away and make a dance"},{"time":879425,"text":"for yourself, and if not that,"},{"time":881378,"text":"at least misbehave more beautifully, more often."}]},{"cues":[{"time":883605,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"},{"time":886223,"text":"Thank you. Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":890953,"text":"Here we go. (Applause)"},{"time":893264,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}